                            <comment id="13101218" author="jbellis" created="Fri, 9 Sep 2011 14:04:28 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;patch to remove allocator.size() from getLiveSize calculation.  also adds note about arena allocation to NEWS.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13101446" author="stuhood" created="Fri, 9 Sep 2011 18:33:13 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Using both currentThroughput and allocator.size is definitely wrong... don&apos;t know what I was thinking there.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Since this was the only code using SlabAllocator.size(), here&apos;s a patch to remove it.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13101451" author="stuhood" created="Fri, 9 Sep 2011 18:35:12 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;+1.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
